♪ Gather 'round
while I sing you ♪

51:41.724 --> 51:43.768
♪ Of Wernher von Braun ♪

51:43.810 --> 51:46.062
♪ A man whose allegiance ♪

51:46.103 --> 51:48.272
♪ Is ruled by expedience ♪

51:48.314 --> 51:51.776
♪ Call him a Nazi,
he won't even frown ♪

51:51.818 --> 51:56.030
♪ "Nazi, Schmazi"
says Wernher von Braun ♪

51:59.033 --> 52:02.453
♪ Don't say
that he's hypocritical ♪

52:02.495 --> 52:06.415
♪ Say rather
that he's apolitical ♪

52:06.457 --> 52:09.710
♪ "Once the rockets are up, who
cares where they come down?" ♪

52:11.796 --> 52:16.342
♪ "That's not my department"
say Wernher von Braun. ♪

52:34.527 --> 52:38.364
Hello, Wernher.

52:38.406 --> 52:40.032
Hello.

52:40.074 --> 52:42.869
How are you?

52:44.328 --> 52:48.499
Can you imagine
our eyes seeing you?

52:48.541 --> 52:50.167
You are a ghost.

52:50.209 --> 52:51.919
I don't want any trouble.

52:51.961 --> 52:55.756
Give Rocket Man a chair
to sit in.

53:06.392 --> 53:08.352
So, Wernher,

53:08.394 --> 53:11.439
do you really believe

53:11.480 --> 53:15.318
that landing
on the moon was worth

53:15.359 --> 53:20.197
the lives of millions of people?

53:22.199 --> 53:25.953
The science...
that I created led

53:25.995 --> 53:28.331
to great inventions,

53:28.372 --> 53:30.791
led to medical innovation,

53:30.833 --> 53:33.169
to longer lives,

53:33.210 --> 53:35.963
to peace around the world.

53:36.005 --> 53:39.175
My work always was one
for peace... and progress.

53:39.216 --> 53:40.760
Shut the fuck up!

53:40.801 --> 53:42.762
Hey, enough. Enough.

53:42.803 --> 53:45.056
Listen,
we've heard it all before.

53:45.097 --> 53:46.390
"I didn't know
what I was doing."

53:46.432 --> 53:47.642
"I was just
following orders."

53:47.683 --> 53:49.060
"I'm sorry for what I did."

53:49.101 --> 53:50.821
"I thought we were building
a better world."

53:50.853 --> 53:52.605
We've heard 'em all.
All the reasons.

53:52.647 --> 53:54.607
All the excuses.

53:54.649 --> 53:57.568
You did horrible fucking things.

53:57.610 --> 53:59.779
You enslaved hundreds of people.

53:59.820 --> 54:02.114
You killed thousands
with your weapons.

54:03.866 --> 54:05.576
Then you come
to the United States.

54:05.618 --> 54:07.578
You live a life of celebrity,

54:07.620 --> 54:10.873
sipping mai tais, gargling
Walt Disney's Jew-hating balls.

54:10.915 --> 54:12.917
We don't need another excuse.

54:12.959 --> 54:14.835
We don't need
another fucking lie.

54:14.877 --> 54:18.255
We are spent.

54:20.257 --> 54:21.884
Now you're gonna
skip the bullshit,

54:21.926 --> 54:23.636
and you're gonna
give us an answer.

54:23.678 --> 54:25.638
What do you know
about the Fourth Reich?

54:26.973 --> 54:29.517
- The what?
- The what? The what?

54:29.558 --> 54:31.078
The Fourth Reich.
What do you know about it?

54:31.102 --> 54:32.704
What do you know
about the fucking Fourth Reich?

54:32.728 --> 54:35.314
I don't understand.

54:35.356 --> 54:37.149
Don't play fucking stupid.
What do you know

54:37.191 --> 54:38.591
- about the Fourth Reich?
- I swear!

54:42.279 --> 54:44.782
I swear.

55:03.300 --> 55:05.553
So Schidler Corp.'s been
in the news

55:05.594 --> 55:07.388
on this South American
trade bill.

55:07.430 --> 55:09.432
Was a guy named Biff Simpson
behind it,

55:09.473 --> 55:11.434
the Under Secretary of State.

55:11.475 --> 55:13.644
And wouldn't you know,
he's on the fucking lam,

55:13.686 --> 55:16.272
chief suspect
in a double homicide.

55:16.313 --> 55:19.025
That guy whose family
was murdered at that barbecue?

55:19.066 --> 55:21.027
Everyone but him,
and not only that.

55:21.068 --> 55:23.070
There was a woman killed,
a Helen Kirsch.

55:23.112 --> 55:25.948
She's a survivor
of the Nazi death camps.

55:25.990 --> 55:28.993
So where's Biff Simpson up here?

55:49.555 --> 55:51.724
Been a long time, friend-o.

55:59.482 --> 56:01.400
Now, Wernher.

56:01.442 --> 56:04.653
You need to tell us everything
you know.

56:07.364 --> 56:09.366
Or we're gonna light you up...

56:09.408 --> 56:12.244
brighter than the stars above.

56:15.372 --> 56:18.250
What is the Fourth Reich?

56:18.292 --> 56:20.753
I don't know.

56:26.592 --> 56:29.220
Hold it, Joe.

56:31.555 --> 56:34.016
Let the boy do it.

56:40.606 --> 56:42.608
It's for the light.

56:52.409 --> 56:54.411
Mm.

57:06.090 --> 57:08.425
What is the Fourth Reich?

57:08.467 --> 57:10.678
I said I don't know.

57:17.059 --> 57:19.019
Well, I don't believe you.

57:19.061 --> 57:21.063
Maybe this will help you
remember.

57:23.107 --> 57:25.192
You sure about that?

57:25.234 --> 57:27.153
Huh?

57:27.194 --> 57:29.780
- Hmm.
- What is the Fourth Reich?

57:29.822 --> 57:31.782
- I don't understand.
- What is the Fourth Reich?

57:31.824 --> 57:34.451
What is the Fourth Reich?

57:35.494 --> 57:37.329
No?

57:37.371 --> 57:41.458
Okay.

57:41.500 --> 57:45.421
What is... the Fourth Reich?

57:45.462 --> 57:47.715
Tell us what you know.

57:47.756 --> 57:49.550
Tell us

57:49.592 --> 57:51.635
- what you fucking know!
- Stop. Please. Please?

57:51.677 --> 57:54.763
I'll tell you!
I'll tell you.

58:02.479 --> 58:04.899
I didn't know the extent.

58:06.400 --> 58:09.361
I only joined
because she promised

58:09.403 --> 58:11.322
there would be no money issues.

58:11.363 --> 58:15.159
The Fourth Reich would fund
projects the prudes at NASA

58:15.201 --> 58:19.496
never would dare... Mars,
distant galaxies, black holes.

58:19.538 --> 58:23.459
She said that if I helped her
take the world,

58:23.500 --> 58:25.586
I could rule the stars.

58:25.628 --> 58:28.297
She?

58:28.339 --> 58:30.299
"The Colonel."

58:30.341 --> 58:31.967
The Colonel?

58:32.009 --> 58:33.928
I-I don't know her real name.

58:33.969 --> 58:36.430
I didn't want to hurt anyone.

58:36.472 --> 58:38.432
I just...

58:38.474 --> 58:42.269
I wanted the moon.

58:42.311 --> 58:44.647
I wanted the stars.

58:44.688 --> 58:47.524
So...

58:47.566 --> 58:49.693
I helped them...

58:49.735 --> 58:51.695
create it.

58:51.737 --> 58:54.365
The Solution.

58:54.406 --> 58:57.159
Wait. The pathogen.
The pathogen, right?

58:57.201 --> 58:59.370
Where is it being released?

58:59.411 --> 59:01.372
Where are they fucking
releasing it?!

59:01.413 --> 59:03.165
Everywhere.

59:03.207 --> 59:06.001
It's in everything.

59:06.043 --> 59:09.505
It's in food and drink,
medicines.

59:09.546 --> 59:11.924
It's a new creation.

59:11.966 --> 59:15.261
It's a new weapon.

59:15.302 --> 59:17.388
A food substitute soon

59:17.429 --> 59:22.059
to be on every shelf in America.

59:22.101 --> 59:24.520
Targeting the inner cities.

59:24.561 --> 59:28.732
Glucopyranose monohydrate.

59:29.775 --> 59:32.319
Corn syrup.

59:34.989 --> 59:37.157
Corn syrup.

59:38.534 --> 59:40.577
Corn syrup.

59:45.874 --> 59:48.002
Like that? You like that?

59:48.043 --> 59:49.980
- What are you doing?
- Tell us what you fucking know...
He's lying.

59:50.004 --> 59:52.023
-Tell us what you know.
Tell us everything.
-Swear...

